OL,3,CSheffield school brawl 'result of
OL,4,Ccommunity tensions', principal says
OL,6,FA brawl at a school in Sheffield
OL,7,Fstemmed from "recent community
OL,8,Ftensions", the principal has told
OL,9,Fparents.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to Fir Vale
OL,12,FAcademy in the city on Thursday after
OL,13,Fa fight broke out amongst students,
OL,14,Fleaving a number of staff and pupils
OL,15,Fhurt.
OL,17,FA letter issued to parents by the
OL,18,Facademy's principal claimed the fight
OL,19,Fhad been the result of recent
OL,20,Ftensions, and that they would ensure
OL,21,Fthose responsible would be dealt with.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
