CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772294631
OL,3,CSheffield school brawl 'result of
OL,4,Ccommunity tensions', principal says
OL,6,FA staff member was reportedly
OL,7,Fhospitalised following the fracas,
OL,8,Fthough police confirmed on Friday that
OL,9,Fnobody was seriously injured.
OL,11,FPrincipal Danny Bullock wrote in the
OL,12,Fletter: "Whilst taking place within
OL,13,Fschool, the incident stemmed from
OL,14,Frecent community tensions.
OL,16,F"I would like to thank staff and the
OL,17,Fmajority of students who were not
OL,18,Finvolved for their calmness and
OL,19,Fresponsibility during what was an
OL,20,Funsettling event."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
