PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772294631
OL,3,CSheffield school brawl 'result of
OL,4,Ccommunity tensions', principal says
OL,6,FMr Bullock added that the school was
OL,7,F"a place of respect, learning and
OL,8,Fstability" and was "not the
OL,9,Fappropriate forum" for those tensions
OL,10,Fto be addressed.
OL,12,FSouth Yorkshire Police said an
OL,13,Finvestigation was now underway, adding
OL,14,Fthat it would be stepping up patrols
OL,15,Fin the area to reassure fraught locals.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
