PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772294631
OL,3,CSheffield school brawl 'result of
OL,4,Ccommunity tensions', principal says
OL,6,FSuperintendent Paul Ferguson said: "We
OL,7,Fknow that this incident has caused
OL,8,Fsome concern in the community ` our
OL,9,Fofficers who are in the area have
OL,10,Freported the streets being quieter
OL,11,Fthan usual.
OL,13,F"We are working closely with the
OL,14,Fschool and other services which engage
OL,15,Fwith young people to ensure
OL,16,Fintelligence from younger generations
OL,17,Fis gathered and any concerns they have
OL,18,Fare addressed, but we would like to
OL,19,Fhear from anyone who can give us an
OL,20,Finsight into this.
OL,26,@nD@dOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
