PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772294631
OL,3,CSheffield school brawl 'result of
OL,4,Ccommunity tensions', principal says
OL,6,F"Our investigation is ongoing and,
OL,7,Fwith both pupils and staff being hurt,
OL,8,Fwe are committed to working with the
OL,9,Fschool and the Youth Justice Service
OL,10,Fto ensure appropriate action is taken
OL,11,Fagainst those who encourage or
OL,12,Fparticipate in disorder.
OL,14,F"We all have the right to feel safe in
OL,15,Four communities and, it goes without
OL,16,Fsaying, young people should feel safe
OL,17,Fat school. We hope the local community
OL,18,Fwill work with us to ensure this."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@bO]
